PrecisRe-appointment of KENNETH R. NURSE, of Regina, Saskatchewan, as Chairman of the Board of Directors of the Canada Ports Corporation to hold office during pleasure for a term of six months, effective July 1, 2000 or until the dissolution of the Canada Ports Corporation, whichever is earlier.

precis:
